   ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ *@
<section class="hero-grand">
    <div class="owl">🦉</div>
    <h1>
        <span class="hero-line">Open-source news trading.</span>
        <span class="hero-line">Built to be inspected.</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="tagline">
        Owlnest is an open-source trading bot that watches financial news, scores catalysts with AI,
        records every decision, and routes paper trades through your own Alpaca account.
    </p>
    <p class="subtag">
        Run it yourself, read the code, tune the rules, and replay decisions before trusting a strategy.
        Managed instances are available for people who want the bot hosted and maintained for them.
    </p>
